OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFeeling chilly under cloudy
OL,6,Fskies, with outbreaks of rain which
OL,7,Fwill gradually ease through the
OL,8,Fmorning, falling as sleet or snow
OL,9,Facross the Pennines. Becoming largely
OL,10,Fdry through the afternoon but
OL,11,Fremaining cloudy. Breezy initially,
OL,12,Fbut winds soon falling light.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA cold night with variable
OL,15,Fcloud, clear spells and a widespread
OL,16,Ffrost. A few patches of mist and fog
OL,17,Fmay also develop in any prolonged
OL,18,Fclear skies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
