OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start, early
OL,6,Fmorning mist and fog patches will soon
OL,7,Fclear, giving some initial brightness
OL,8,Fbefore cloud builds again through the
OL,9,Fafternoon with outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fdeveloping.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,13,Fcloudy with patchy drizzle Sunday.
OL,14,FAfter a murky start Monday, brighter
OL,15,Fspells likely to develop along with a
OL,16,Frisk of showers. Some brightness
OL,17,Finitially Tuesday but becoming
OL,18,Fincreasingly cloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
